unittitle_ssm: New York City COVID-19 Web Activism Collection
abstract_ssm: The NYC COVID-19 Web Activism Collection, assembled by Tamiment archivists, documents activism and mutual aid in response to the COVID-19 pandemic, starting in 2020. The collection consists of archived websites on topics such as tenants rights, workers organizing surrounding unsafe working conditions, racism, and decarceration.
